 NOW WE HAVE 100% CHANCE OF RAIN AT OKEECHOBEE. PERFORMANCE IN THE HARSHEST CONDITIONS AND THIS SUIT KEEPS ME WARM, DRY AND COMFORTABLE ALL DAY LONG. IT'S THE ONE PIECE OF EQUIPMENT I NEVER LEAVE HOME WITHOUT.\"<\/strong><\/h3>","size":"text-size-large"}},"text_CYbbwz":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>- Lee Livesay, Bassmaster Elite Angler<\/em><\/p>","size":"text-size-regular"}}},"block_order":["heading_GPMgaC","text_GH3bLP","text_CYbbwz"],"settings":{"id":"","text_width":"xlarge","text_position":"left","text_alignment":"left","color_bg":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","color_heading":"#1a1c1d","color_text":"#2c2d2e","color_links":"#2c2d2e","full_bleed_layout":false,"disable_top_spacing":false,"disable_bottom_spacing":true}},"background_video_4Uy4qw":{"type":"background-video","settings":{"desktop_height":"desktop-height-450","mobile_height":"mobile-height-500","full_width":true,"video_controls":true,"video":"","video_hosted":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/Pro-Rain-Video.mp4","overlay_color":"#000000","overlay_opacity":0,"disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":false}},"rich_text_L7gQWK":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_Tw8bD4":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"NO EXCUSES. NO LIMITS. JUST RESULTS.","marker_style":"style1","size":"h3","marker_color":"#fd6262"}},"text_83naPd":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>When the storm rolls in, the real anglers don’t head for cover—they dig in and fish harder. The NEW Pro Series is built for those who refuse to let brutal conditions dictate their day on the water. Designed with elite performance in mind, this full suit is crafted from premium Toray 3L stretch nylon, reinforced with abrasion-resistant panels where it matters most. With an unmatched 30K waterproof rating and fully seam-sealed construction, you stay bone dry no matter how relentless the rain gets, keeping you ready for anything, whether you're grinding out a tournament day or chasing giants off the grid.<\/p>","size":"text-size-regular"}}},"block_or